### Bazel ###
# Output symlinks Bazel creates at the workspace root. Scoped with a
# leading slash so the pattern doesn't match nvidia-internal/bazel-build.md
# or other paths containing `bazel-` further down the tree.
/bazel-*
.bazel-cache/
user.bazelrc

